---
title: Moroccan-Spiced Lamb Chops with Harissa Roasted Potatoes and Lemon Yogurt Sauce
description: Spice up your life with these succulent lamb chops rubbed in Moroccan Spice Blend! A zippy lemon yogurt sauce adds cooling contrast to harissa-spiced potatoes.
